para_trans: GOVERNMENT ORDER NUMBER: MARAGRAN-2024 / P.No.132 / E-837175 / GR.
To join the post transferred by the Director of Libraries, Maharashtra State, Mumbai in accordance with this order.
The employees should be relieved of their present duties with immediate effect. Also, the officers who have been transferred immediately
Join the post of transferor and submit the report to the Government through the Directorate of Libraries.
Since the transfer of the employees concerned is being done as per their request, they are entitled to a period of retention, travel allowance and
No daily allowance will be paid.
